掉走曬啲裝冇得重用<br />\n先至有機會可以同班仆街談判"},{"pid":"ec0651aef90f2b49a96b48af32670b11602b1a6d","tid":1876600,"uid":25743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:34:56.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲安排人地各國係出唔到手干預，人地資源點安排係人地國家嘅事，呢啲嘢根本只能口術，強烈譴責之外可以做到啲咩？<br />\n等如人地一間公司財政，資源點分配係人地公司決策，人地可以起反常態安排都可以，第三者可以點對你？對你做呢啲嘢佢又有咩得益驅使佢要咁做？<br />\n可唔可以比到具體內容令佢地咁做？<br />\n如果真係唔想佢哋出事，你自己有無諗到我地自己可以做到反抗嘅事？我哋自己內部改變，唔係望天打掛，求東求西？人哋願意幫手唔係下下可以做到爸娘咁保護你地，我哋自己有冇勇氣做到「時代革命」呢四隻字。<br />\n革命係反社會主義，係犯罪，要解決問題就可唔可以二百萬人一齊攻全港警察？搶返我地香港自己嘅資源比醫護，可以同政府搶世界嘅資源逼政府資源用盡跪低，用滲透政治權力從中搶返權力？<br />\n當香港人未有呢個覺悟，做一切都係送頭，香港人未做到解決自私，分化，內鬥，突破道德高地，自我束縛一切事情都係無意義<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V7Aoedg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV7Aoedg.jpg&h=74f8f0db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzKHuME.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzKHuME.png&h=18d79ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAFSRZ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAFSRZ2.png&h=ff1d41eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CdAfPMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdAfPMM.png&h=ec47cce4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCxh26N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCxh26N.jpg&h=d4abbe4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uq7qsys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuq7qsys.jpg&h=60ac432f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以我不了<br />\n如果香港人明白到以下嘅話，未來先有希望<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sSeHuNP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsSeHuNP.jpg&h=f89cffc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceKHuNQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceKHuNQ.jpg&h=0418f922&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A2Y89NR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA2Y89NR.jpg&h=48e3b523&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/powyBsR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpowyBsR.jpg&h=078dd0cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PALszx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PALszx.jpg&h=665e8ef2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ToSRn7T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FToSRn7T.jpg&h=7dbf77c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4R6WsU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4R6WsU.jpg&h=e4d1ccc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFGbn7V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFGbn7V.jpg&h=a8a6c25a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2cd5a76a921f930b679b5ea584c2055642934be","tid":1876600,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243aec666fa8d8ec1358cf827af0020e8f0ee7ca","tid":1876600,"uid":259674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:37:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"981dc99c9e98fc826cfb9126040129e33382261a","tid":1876600,"uid":34755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1560f10a0bbd786c747b5a91b4c74b469cd04c9","tid":1876600,"uid":155793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1156926b556121c5ea3fb68ed5d1051388af5e06","tid":1876600,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5d28609284e2c61430752e77bde81217eb48aba","tid":1876600,"uid":155793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:23:39.000Z","msg":"推一"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:44:40.000Z","msg":"係 好似烏克蘭後期咁樣全部警察家屬可以配槍 任射殺人都得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"你容許得今日佢地有罩<br />\n聽日佢就休班佩槍<br />\n後日全家都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:38:32.000Z","msg":"所以要係家屬未有前 落手"},{"pid":